{"tid":1349171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"石鏡泉話有人利用佢言論黎攻擊他人喎","createTime":"2019-07-22T09:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T13:04:37.000Z","uid":30524,"like":1,"dislike":142,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"ff801b045c05c658b88de5eee5f9f45ea6f1b3ec","tid":1349171,"uid":30524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3S03KL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3S03KL.png&h=5b2ffa6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內部聲明<br />\n<br />\n經濟日報集團一向支持社會透過以和平、理性及非暴力去表達訴求。理解近期社會上出現不同聲音及對前景的憂慮，希望事件能儘快平息。我們反對並嚴厲譴責任何暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n公司就石Sir最近言論及元朗事件，已經與他開會，石Sir會盡快作澄清:<br />\n<br />\n1) 石Sir強調，自己一直反對暴力，支持和平理性表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n2) 石Sir今次出席守護香港的言論，只屬個人意見，並不代表公司立場。<br />\n<br />\n3) 就昨天元朗發生的事件，石Sir強調他毫不知情，也不是他所預計的事，抱歉有人利用他的言論，作攻擊別人借口。<br />\n<br />\n4) 石Sir重申編採部一向以事實為根基，秉持三公(公平、公正、公道)及中肯原則。<br />\n<br />\n企業傳訊部"},{"pid":"6569da528d7ef11054458a9207970e58e635931c","tid":1349171,"uid":30524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628d28fce4b98393c70c211b820bb7d16f2b7189","tid":1349171,"uid":5787,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"屌你喇死老野！<br />\n你根本就係幕後操縱"},{"pid":"9569d6734920aa4b58ae66a0d0bf4c91371b9d33","tid":1349171,"uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:47:29.000Z","msg":"自己叫人打人 點利用？"},{"pid":"77baaa88c94cf2efa2f9008d96a23dc9bf788af8","tid":1349171,"uid":5787,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"又水喉通、又藤條<br />\n你講既全部都出現晒"},{"pid":"09fd07ffd5d467b03f080a9656450b82f6d29f02","tid":1349171,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"痴線"},{"pid":"07e597ad0f34deb48ca5d1fec538aee42a6c4461","tid":1349171,"uid":30524,"like":1,"dislike"